T1  - EVOLUTIONARY CONSUMERS IMPLY MONOPOLIES EXIT
AU  - Hummel, Patrick
AU  - McAfee, R. Preston
Y1  - 2018/11/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12318
