T1  - GOVERNMENT DEBT AND BANKING FRAGILITY: THE SPREADING OF STRATEGIC UNCERTAINTY
AU  - Cooper, Russell
AU  - Nikolov, Kalin
Y1  - 2018/11/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12323
